# 2026-07-08 21:45:57.387555
+Add structured logging to sarmkadan/dotnet-feature-flags.
+Work in: /home/redrocket/task-factory/workdir/dotnet-feature-flags
+
+1. Ensure Microsoft.Extensions.Logging is used (add ILogger<T> injection if missing)
+2. Add meaningful log messages to key operations:
+   - LogInformation for successful operations
+   - LogWarning for recoverable issues
+   - LogError for failures (with exception)
+   - LogDebug for detailed flow info
+3. Use structured logging with named parameters: _logger.LogInformation("Processing {ItemId}", item.Id)
+4. Do NOT add logging to every single method - only key entry/exit points and error paths
+
+Commit as: "feat: add structured logging"
+
